latestIgtvVideos.title: Happy 30th Jenna!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wow 30 years. 3 decades on earth. And you’re just getting started! @jennagiesow what you’ve accomplished and done in 30 years on this planet, most people would dream to accomplish in a lifetime. You are loved by so many and truly are an inspiration to all.  The example that you lead by touches so many. 

I sent out a message to some of Jenna’s close family and friends to wish her a happy birthday, and here’s what everyone sent back. I think everyone agrees that you’re pretty amazing! You’re kind, funny, smart, gracious, and an incredible mama! I love you to the moon and back and I am so thankful to walk through life together. Here’s to the next 30! Happy birthday Love!

latestIgtvVideos.title: CK turns 2!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I cannot believe my little girl is 2 years old today! Happy birthday Charlee Kay! You’re momma and I love you so much! HBD princess!

latestIgtvVideos.title: RHEMA LIGHTS • a VAST MEDIA film
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Man, 2020 couldn’t haven’t ended with a better project. I was contacted by a client and was tasked with capturing the Rhema Christmas Lights. Hold up, let me back up...

@rbtc_usa is actually what brought me from Michigan to Tulsa in 2015. My two years at Rhema were so pivotal for me personally and spiritually. Now five years later, I’m married, a Dad, and a business owner of a media company in Tulsa (@vast__media) and I was asked to capture the place that captured my heart.

Their Christmas lights are so special and if you haven’t experienced them for yourself, you’ve got two more days.

Also, huge shout out to @skylarhagin for leading the charge and making the light shine a little brighter this year!

Happy Birthday Charlee!
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Charlee Kay -

What can I say? This past year has been the most life changing so far. God has expanded my heart so much for you little one. Watching you grow up, and light bulbs pop on daily, your laugh, your smile, those blue eyes. I don’t think it’s possible for your momma and I to love you any more. What a year it’s been! HAPPY BIRTHDAY PEANUT! You’re ONE!! ☝🏼 🎂 🎉

latestIgtvVideos.title: VAST Media 2019 Recap
latestIgtvVideos.caption: When the ball dropped last year, I had no idea what 2019 truly would have in store. I would take the biggest leap of my life and leave my comfortable 9-5 job and set out to launch a company [@vast__media ] I had no real professional experience in. I have to admit, with hard work and some determination, the American dream is still very much alive. Biggest shout out to my family. Without your love, support, and sacrifice, I wouldn’t be doing what I’m doing today. Also huge shout out to @crotzie @dillonayoung @madawoo. You guys are the real dream team. Thanks for the killer memories 2019, but the best is still yet to come!

latestPosts.caption:
Just a casual stroll past the Plaza Hotel on 5th Ave… half-expecting someone to yell ‘Kevin?!’ 👀 🚶🏻‍♂️ 🏢

No sign of him, but I did find light, shadow, and rhythm in the streets. Across from the iconic Plaza Hotel, the gilded statue of General Sherman catches light like fire. Gold against gray. The streets of Manhattan swirl around it, but for a moment, everything pauses. 

All photos straight out of camera on the Fujifilm X100VI using Classic Cuban Negative (clean).

📍Grand Army Plaza, Manhattan
🪙 William Tecumseh Sherman Monument by Augustus Saint-Gaudens
📸 Fujifilm X100VI | SOOC
🎞 Classic Cuban Negative (Clean) by @osanbilgi

latestPosts.caption:
One camera. One city. One rockstar.
And somehow I got the invite to be in the room for all of it. 🎤📸

This week, @todayshow brought me back out — this time to capture @machinegunkelly lighting up Rockefeller Plaza in the heart of NYC. First time in the city. First time VIP. First time shooting a live show like this… and man, I’m still buzzing.

All frames shot straight out of camera — no edits, just vibes and film simulations I couldn’t wait to unload back at the hotel.

If there’s one thing I learned about MGK, he shows up for the fans.

Big stage energy, bigger heart. Dude throws down like a rock legend but loves like a hometown hero.

Drop your favorite MGK song in the comments ⬇️🎶

 @carsondaly @craigmelvinnbc @savannahguthrie @jennabhager @angielassman @alroker @kevinschatell @dylandreyernbc 

—

There’s a rhythm to Central Park you can’t hear in photos. 🔊🍃🏙️

Hooves echo off cobblestone. Laughter cuts through tree cover. Birds call from above while the city hums just beyond.
I wandered through Strawberry Fields, where John Lennon and Yoko Ono used to walk. Beatles songs drifted from a nearby musican, and for a moment, the whole place felt like a memory.

My first walk through the park felt both new and strangely familiar.

Still stuck at $15K/month? 

You’ve got a job, not a business. We’re bringing the best in the industry together in LA to show you how to scale to $100K/month—and beyond. Systems, scripts, and the blueprint from agency owners doing $80K–$300K/month. 

If you can’t make it to LA, no problem. Comment MASTERMIND to get access to two free workshops that’ll put you on the fast track.

Zink Lake murals, finally up close. 📷 💥 🎨 
Color poured across concrete,
stories stretched along the river.
Tulsa feels grandour because of it.

All images straight out of the Fuji X100VI,
Classic Cuban Negative clean 🎞️ 

5 min after taking these shots, 50 mph winds, lightning, and rain rolled in. 🌧️ ⚡️

Peek-a-boo University Park Tower in the mix.
Artists tagged below — they earned it. 🏆
